history.content:
Please join us for our next undergrad social hour, 3/21 from 3:30-4:30 in the Wozniak Lounge, 430 Soda Hall.
 

There is no formal program for this event, but faculty will be available to chat about whatever is on your mind in small groups.  There are still topics from the original Town Hall meeting that we are planning to discuss.  At this time we are are working on different options for these conversations with campus leadership.  Come enjoy delicious food, mingle with your peers and chat with faculty!
history.subject: Undergrad Social Hour, 3/21 3:30-4:30pm in Woz
